    <releaseNotes>'Merged PR 10312: [VMIN] DDG VminTC into PRIME'
'Merged PR 7934: Force projects to fail if they reference other projects that are not required.'
'Merged PR 7839: [PrimeScanHRYSSNTestMethod] Shift PinMapping file to test method for independent SSN network'
'Merged PR 7891: Cleanup unneeded Project references'
'Merged PR 7540: Prime single solution'
'Merged PR 7574: Applying V13Conversion to the SampleTP'
'Merged PR 7531: Seperating the MetaNuget from TestMethodResources'</releaseNotes>
